# Port source cache — NOT committed.
#
# The build scripts under tools/ports/ download each upstream tarball here on
# demand (curl-if-absent) from its OFFICIAL distribution URL, extract it, and
# patch the tree. We deliberately do NOT vendor the tarballs: it wastes git
# space and it is better to rely on the official upstream source. A fresh build
# fetches them; the tarballs and the extracted trees are all build artifacts.
#
# (build-libiconv.sh needs no tarball — it builds a self-written iconv stub.)
#
# Ignore everything here except this file.
*
!.gitignore
